Day 106: Dived into One-Hot Encoding & its variations.

Creates binary columns for each category—no false ordering.
Great for categorical data without hierarchy… but can explode your dataset if categories are too many.

Lesson: Choosing the wrong encoding isn’t harmless—it can confuse your model, waste memory, and tank accuracy.

